
Debian-based Systems ( Ubuntu, Linux Mint)

APT (Advanced Package Tool)
Update Package List:
sudo apt update


Install a Package:
sudo apt install package-name


Example (Installing unzip, jq, and wget):
sudo apt update
sudo apt install unzip jq wget


Remove a Package:
sudo apt remove package-name



Red Hat-based Systems ( RHEL, CentOS, Fedora)



YUM (Yellowdog Updater Modified) or DNF (Dandified YUM)
Update Package List:

For YUM:
sudo yum check-update

Example (Installing unzip, jq, and wget):

sudo yum install unzip jq wget
